    "headline": "Thermo Fisher Scientific Announces Quarterly Dividend",
    "summary": "WALTHAM, Mass., July 09, 2026--Thermo Fisher Scientific Inc. (NYSE: TMO), the world leader in serving science, today announced that its Board of Directors authorized a quarterly cash dividend of $0.47 per common share, payable on October 15, 2026, to shareholders of record as of September 15, 2026.",
